    "description": "CLI script that seeds all RNGs, runs a deterministic heavy-tailed toy experiment comparing sample mean vs median-of-means, and writes outputs/results.json and outputs/figure.png to a fixed schema.",
    "category": "source"
  },
  {
    "path": "src/estimators.py",
    "description": "Implements deterministic estimators (sample mean and median-of-means) and supporting utilities used by the toy experiment.",
